[I] A classic dynamic tiling Wayland compositor

[T] river-classic is a dynamic tiling Wayland compositor with flexible runtime
[T] configuration. It is a fork of river 0.3 intended for users that are happy
[T] with how river 0.3 works and do not wish to deal with the majorly breaking
[T] changes planned for the river 0.4.0 release.

[U] https://isaacfreund.com/software/river/

[A] Isaac Freund <mail@isaacfreund.com>
